{"id":4585,"date":"2018-10-19T18:04:40","date_gmt":"2018-10-19T22:04:40","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/course-quebec-montreal-de-loption-sens\/"},"modified":"2023-06-14T13:19:15","modified_gmt":"2023-06-14T17:19:15","slug":"course-quebec-montreal-de-loption-sens","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/course-quebec-montreal-de-loption-sens\/","title":{"rendered":"Course Qu\u00e9bec-Montr\u00e9al de l&rsquo;Option SENS"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Le 13 octobre dernier, les 29 \u00e9tudiantes et \u00e9tudiants, les professeurs de l&rsquo;Option SENS (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/programmes\/sciences-humaines\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">programme des sciences humaines<\/a>) ainsi que des parents b\u00e9n\u00e9voles ont r\u00e9alis\u00e9 le d\u00e9fi de courir les 280 kilom\u00e8tres qui s\u00e9parent le Parlement de Qu\u00e9bec et le c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent. L&rsquo;objectif de la course \u00e9tait d&rsquo;amasser des fonds pour financer le stage en Bolivie qui aura lieu aux mois de mai et juin 2019.<\/p>\n<p>Non seulement le d\u00e9fi physique des 280 km a \u00e9t\u00e9 relev\u00e9, mais l&rsquo;objectif de financement de 5000\u00a0$ a \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9pass\u00e9! Au total, c&rsquo;est plus de 6000\u00a0$ qui ont \u00e9t\u00e9 r\u00e9colt\u00e9s.<\/p>\n<p>Les \u00e9tudiantes et \u00e9tudiants ainsi que les professeurs de l&rsquo;Option SENS remercient chaleureusement les donatrices et donateurs ainsi que les parents b\u00e9n\u00e9voles pr\u00e9sents lors de la course.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Le 13 octobre dernier s&rsquo;est d\u00e9roul\u00e9e la 5<sup>e<\/sup> \u00e9dition de la course \u00e0 relais Qu\u00e9bec-Montr\u00e9al organis\u00e9e par les \u00e9tudiantes et \u00e9tudiants de l&rsquo;Option SENS (programme de sciences humaines).<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":4586,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[195],"etiquette-interne":[2287,2315],"class_list":["post-4585","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle","sujet-actualite-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-sciences-humaines"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:43:37","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4585","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4585"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4585\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4901,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4585\/revisions\/4901"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4586"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4585"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4585"},{"taxonomy":"sujet-actualite","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/sujet-actualite?post=4585"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=4585"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/ap